# Implementation Plan — Finance & Accounting Portal Expansion

Massive upgrade to both the **Admin Portal** and **Accounting Portal** with premium dark-mode dashboards matching the reference UI designs.

---

## Architecture Overview

```
[Admin Portal :5174]
  └── /pos       → POS & Fee Management (redesigned)
  └── /finance   → Accounts Overview (redesigned)

[Accounting Portal :5176]
  └── /              → Accounts Overview Dashboard
  └── /pos-fees      → POS & Fee Management
  └── /ledger        → General Ledger + Trial Balance
  └── /journal       → Transaction Journal
  └── /invoices      → Invoice Management (redesigned)
  └── /expenses      → Expense Manager
  └── /budget        → Budget Tracker
  └── /cashflow      → Cash Flow Report
  └── /reports       → Reports Hub (P&L, Income vs Expense, Student-wise, Audit Logs)
  └── /reconciliation → Bank Reconciliation (existing)
```

